                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(center)\">\n                                        <placeName>S. Marshfield Mass</placeName>\n                                        <date>July 1 1849</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(10)\">Dear Sir! You would</p>\n                              <p>oblige your subscriber if you would be kind <sic>enogh</sic> to\n                                        give me <sic>infamation</sic><lb/>\n                                        <sic>wether</sic> you have <sic>recived</sic> from\n                                                  <persName>Mr <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                                                  >Marmser</hi></persName> of\n                                                  <placeName>Boston</placeName> the subscription\n                                                  <sic>mony</sic><lb/> with three Dollars for your\n                                                  <hi rend=\"underline\">Occident</hi>\n                                        <sic>wich</sic> I have paid to him <date><sic>Aprill</sic>\n                                                  1848</date><lb/> I have subt through <persName>M\n                                                  Marmser</persName> for your Occ't and\n                                                  <sic>recived</sic> the same from\n                                                  <date>January</date><lb/> at <persName>E\n                                                  Marshfield</persName> monthly regular when I\n                                        removed to <placeName>N. York</placeName> I\n                                                  <sic>orderet</sic> your Perio<lb/>dical through\n                                                  <persName>Mr. T I Seixas</persName> to\n                                                  <placeName>355 Grand St.</placeName> in\n                                                  <date><sic>Aprill</sic> 1849</date>\n                                        <persName>Mr Young</persName>\n                                        <sic>besendet</sic> a<lb/> Bill from <date>1848</date>\n                                        <sic>wich</sic> I paid him also with Three Dollars I have\n                                        also paid Six Dollars<lb/> for the Occt and have only\n                                                  <sic>recived</sic> it for one year and four\n                                                  <sic>monts</sic><lb/> I am sorry to say that\n                                                  <persName>M young</persName> has not left the Occt\n                                        since <date><sic>Aprill</sic></date><lb/> I value your Occ't\n                                        much but circumstance obliges me to discontinue after<lb/>\n                                        my term has expired, if, I am entitled to your Occ't till\n                                                  <date>January <hi rend=\"underline\"\n                                                  >1850</hi></date><lb/> I wish to have the same\n                                        left monthly in care of <persName>M. Ehrenberg</persName>\n                                        <placeName>355 Grand St. N. Y.</placeName><lb/> but if you\n                                        have not received the <sic>mony</sic> from <persName><hi\n                                                  rend=\"underline\">Mr</hi> Warmser</persName>.\n                                                  <placeName>Boston</placeName><lb/> please to\n                                        inform me of it you will much oblige</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(10)\">Your Obt <sic>Servand</sic></p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(11)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">Gerson Frank</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(11)\"> at <placeName>S. Marshfield</placeName></p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(12)\">\n                                        <placeName>\n                                                  <hi rend=\"underline\">Massachusetts</hi>\n                                        </placeName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>To the <addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>!</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Editor of the Occident</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(2 )\">\n                                        <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n                              </p>"
                  },
